  "body": "It would be nice to add a check list step to recreate the keystore and deposit key using the same mnemonic. \r\n\r\n## On the generate keys page\r\n\r\nOn https://launchpad.ethereum.org/generate-keys, I would add the following after\r\n> ⬜ I am keeping my key(s) safe and have written down my mnemonic phrase.\r\n\r\n⬜ I have recreated my keystore and deposit keys using my mnemonic and I have confirmed that they all share the same public key(s).\r\n\r\n## On the checklist page\r\n\r\nOn https://launchpad.ethereum.org/checklist, I would add the following somewhere:\r\n\r\n⬜ I have recreated my keystore from my mnemonic and I have confirmed that all the keystores I created share the same public key(s).\r\n\r\nThose added check list step could have save someone's deposit already and hopefully they can help save someone else's deposit in the future.",
